    <section class="content" id="about">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>The Smiles of Care Initiative is dedicated to supporting individuals with mental health challenges by providing them with free electronic toothbrushes and promoting better oral hygiene. Our program aims to reduce barriers to self-care and create a supportive community for those in need.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="content" id="mission">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>We believe that good oral health is fundamental to overall well-being. By distributing electronic toothbrushes and offering resources to those struggling with mental illness, we aim to enhance their quality of life and boost their self-esteem.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="content" id="get-involved">
